Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:21.60,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}这份愿望却渐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:24.89,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}本已check mate的黑暗仍在持续
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:27.35,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}人类的工作真麻烦啊
